Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/jbkopecky/dotfiles.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Copy '.bash_profile' & '.shell_prompt.sh' to home directory

    cp ~/.vim/.bash_profile ~/
    cp ~/.vim/.shell_prompt.sh ~/
